name: Guys CheckTwice™ Yeti
description: BEFORE BUYING THIS PRODUCT: CheckTwice Clothing™ is currently experimenting with T-Shirt production methods, and CANNOT guarantee a good print life any longer than a one wash. ALTHOUGH, in attempt to preserve the print life turn the T-Shirt inside out in the washing machine, and wash at 30 degrees only. ------ This product is printed onto a White, 100% Cotton T-Shirt, and represented closely to the preview picture. Made from 100% Cotton. The CheckTwice™ Logo is printed in the bottom right hand corner of the T-shirt on the back, it's small so don't worry!!
